    "Name": "New Dawn ND-RR3",
    "Details": "The ND-RR3 is the close-range specialist of the original trio, carrying a Sword as its primary physical threat alongside a Snub-Nose PPC. An ER Large Laser and two Medium Pulse Lasers give it solid ranged capability at short and medium distances. Four Machine Guns spread across the center torso and left arm handle anti-infantry duties and can threaten lightly armored targets. Thirteen and a half tons of armor supports the aggressive close-range doctrine.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Maintain</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.11</color></b>",
